com.ibm.ccl.soa.deploy.core
Class UnitFilter

java.lang.Object
  com.ibm.ccl.soa.deploy.core.UnitFilter

public abstract class UnitFilter
extends java.lang.Object

Provide suggestions for Units that may be hosted by, or a member of, this Unit.

The returned Lists can contain simple Strings, UnitFilter.UnitFilterTemplates, UnitFilter.UnitFilterActions, and Lists of the above. Simple Strings are interpreted by the ResourceTypeService.

Any element is potentially deployable. Clients must describe to the SOA Topology Modeler framework which elements may be deployed using the com.ibm.ccl.soa.deploy.core.unitLifecycle/unitFilter extension point. That extension point requires clients to supply a subclass of UnitFilter. The client implementation will only be invoked when an element matching the expression defined by the client's extension is encountered.

Please refer to the extension point documentation for com.ibm.ccl.soa.deploy.core.unitLifecycle/unitFilter for more information.

Since:
1.0
